    "This process can be expressed as:min 𝑓 𝑑𝑚 E(𝑥) ∼ T [L (𝑓 𝑙𝑙𝑚(𝑥), 𝑓 𝑑𝑚 (𝑥))](1)To optimize the weights in 𝑓 𝑑𝑚, we use cross-entropy as the loss function L to calculate the difference between 𝑓 𝑙𝑙𝑚 (𝑥) and 𝑓 𝑑𝑚 (𝑥) predictions.",
